    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - INSTALL - SHIFTER HOUSING</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>SHIFTER HOUSING</title>
        <para>There are two (2) sizes of bolts. The 1-1/2" bolts are used with the lifting eyes.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the shift bars in the neutral position.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the mainshaft sliding clutches in the neutral position (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p1">Figure 251</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p1" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p1" filename="../figg13/G13017P1.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 251. Mainshaft Sliding Clutches In Neutral Position</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position a new shifter housing gasket on the shifter housing mounting surface (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p2">Figure 252</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p2" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p2" filename="../figg13/G13017P2.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 252. Install Shifter Housing</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">As you install the shifter housing, make sure the yokes fit into the corresponding clutch
                gears slots (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p2">Figure 252</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Apply Eaton/Fuller Sealant #71205 or Loctite 242 to the retaining bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the retaining bolts; tighten to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#8226;m) of torque (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p3">Figure 253</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017p3" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017p3" filename="../figg13/G13017P3.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 253. Install Retaining Bolts</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the washer and nut on the alignment stud (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017p3">Figure 253</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
